def: The state or quality of being inky; blackness.
Of or pertaining to the Koran.
A structure on the hurricane deck of a steamer, containing thepilot house, officers' cabins, etc. [Western U.S.] Knight.
A tribe of North American Indians belonging to the Creekconfederation.
Pertaining to, or derived from, Japheth, one of the sons ofNoah; as, Japhetic nations, the nations of Europe and Northern Asia;Japhetic languages.
An instrument for measuring the evaporation from water, ice, orsnow. Brande & C.
One who strolls from place to place; one who has no settledhabitation; an idle wanderer; a sturdy beggar; an incorrigible rogue;a vagabond.Vagrants and outlaws shall offend thy view. Prior.
A conventional comment or saying, such as those characteristicof bromides. [Slang]
